2. Bundled stock themes (app/linkstack/themes/vendor/)
------------------------------------------------------
Curated LinkStack community themes are vendored unzipped and provenance-pinned
in app/linkstack/themes/themes.lock.json. Each theme retains its own license as
declared in its readme.md. Summary:

    MIT:    Cloudy-Storm, Dark, Dawn, Magic-Kingdom, PaperBold, PolySleek,
            Rainbow, Soothing
    GPLv3:  Aurora, bean-soup, flare, galaxy, llc-vanilla, mono, polygon,
            stargazer, sublime, winter-wonderland

    Excluded on purpose: the upstream themes "SoT" and "minceraft" declare a
    GPLv3 NON-COMMERCIAL-USE-ONLY restriction and are therefore NOT bundled in
    this commercial deployment. Do not re-add them without a licensing review.

Theme authors include JulianPrieber, the LinkStack Team, nekosheen and others.
Several themes build on the Skeleton CSS framework (MIT,
https://github.com/dhg/Skeleton).


